Pre-Game Insights: The Faroe Islands have struggled for results since their strong finish in the 2022 Nations League campaign, most recently suffering a 1-0 defeat to Latvia in the third-place clash of the 2024 Baltic Cup.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This will be just the second meeting between the Faroe Islands and North Macedonia.
Others: North Macedonia have also endured a difficult run of results in recent games and will hope they can find better luck elsewhere this weekend. They were beaten 2-1 by the Czech Republic last time out.
